1.text: Wash and moisturize your face to prep your skin for makeup.

2.text: Apply primer so your foundation goes on well and stays in place.

3.text: Use a sponge to pat and blend matte foundation into your skin.

4.text: Dab concealer under your eyes and on blemishes and blend it well.

5.text: Dust your face with translucent powder to set and mattify your look.

6.text: Pat on some pink blush to highlight your cheekbones.

7.text: Fill in your brows with a matching pencil so they look thin and elongated.

8.text: Dab an eyeshadow primer over your eyelids.

9.text: Dust a dark mauve eyeshadow onto your eyelids with a makeup brush.

10.text: Smudge a thick line of black eyeliner pencil at the outer edges of your lids.

11.text: Outline and define your crease with black eyeshadow.

12.text: Drag a little black eyeshadow underneath your eyes for a sultry look.

13.text: Outline your waterline with black eyeliner, if desired.

14.text: Curl your eyelashes and apply waterproof mascara.

15.text: Outline your lips with concealer to disguise your lip's natural contours.

16.text: Line your lips with pink or red liner and emphasize the cupid's bow.

17.text: Fill in your lips with bright pink or red lipstick.

18.text: Add some lip gloss to make your lip color more shiny, if you want.
